dct_title_s: Nigeria 1:12,500. Ibadan & environs / drawn & reproduced by Federal Surveys, Nigeria, 1960
dct_description_sm: Collection only contains sheet 2. Relief shown by 50 foot contour intervals and spot heights. Revised by Surveyor general Western region, Ibadan up to May 1960. Drawn & reproduced by Federal surveys, Nigeria, 1967. In lower right margin: "200/644/7-67." Map shows boundaries of government's land acquisitions. Shows ward boundaries and numbers.
